  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\"><img alt=\"Stone Crows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/50px-Stone_Crows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/75px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/100px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Conn<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> son of Coratt</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\"><img alt=\"Stone Crows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/50px-Stone_Crows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/75px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/100px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Conn son of Coratt by Amok.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg/350px-Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg/525px-Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg/700px-Conn_son_of_Coratt_by_Amok.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Conn by Amok © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">Green Fork</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coratt\" title=\"Coratt\">Coratt</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Conn</b>, known as <b>Conn son of Coratt</b> because of <a href=\"/index.php/Coratt\" title=\"Coratt\">his father</a>, is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a> found in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Conn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Conn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Conn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Conn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Conn is a handsome man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He is bold<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and friends with <a href=\"/index.php/Shagga\" title=\"Shagga\">Shagga</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Conn is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a> whom <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> first encounter in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>. Tyrion offers to give his hauberk to Conn to secure passage through the mountains, but the Stone Crows insist that all he possesses is already theirs. Tyrion gains them as allies by promising them the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Conn is one of the clansmen who leaves the mountains with Tyrion, and he accompanies Tyrion to the war council held by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Ulf\" title=\"Ulf\">Ulf</a> demands blood money when three Stone Crows kill a <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brother\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Moon Brother\">Moon Brother</a>, but Conn and <a href=\"/index.php/Shagga\" title=\"Shagga\">Shagga</a> refuse to pay. Ulf later drinks <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a> and offers to share oxmeat with Tyrion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">battle on the Green Fork</a>, Tyrion sees Conn's horse kick a man in the ribs. Conn is slain by a spear thrust during the battle, with Tyrion finding Shagga cradling his friend's head by a tree after the fighting.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Conn\">Quotes by Conn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Conn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tyrion</b>: This hauberk I wear is large for me, but it should fit Conn nicely, and the battle-axe I carry would suit <a href=\"/index.php/Shagga\" title=\"Shagga\">Shagga</a>'s mighty hand far better than that wood-axe he holds.<br />\n<b>Conn</b>: The <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">half man</a> would pay us with our own coin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and Conn</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Kevan</b>: By what right do you savages intrude on our councils?<br />\n<b>Conn</b>: Savages, <a href=\"/index.php/Lowlander\" title=\"Lowlander\">lowlander</a>? We are <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">free men</a>, and free men by rights sit on all war councils.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a> and Conn</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tywin</b>: It is said that the men of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">mountain clans</a> are warriors without fear.<br />\n<b>Conn</b>: It is said truly.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> and Conn</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Conn\">Quotes about Conn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Conn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Conn might have been handsome if you washed him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Conn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_62\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 62\">Chapter 62</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403205749\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.097 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.289 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1660/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11039/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11551/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1804/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3883/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.66 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  273.019      1 -total\n 91.10%  248.713      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 90.64%  247.456      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.37%   25.581     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.30%   19.943     12 Template:Ref\n  4.74%   12.930